snippet: The depleted Los Angeles Lakers had to keep Robert Sacre on the court after he fouled out in the fourth quarter of a 119-108 victory at the Cleveland Cavaliers.
abstract: Los Angeles Lakers beat Cleveland Cavaliers, 119-108; other basketball news noted.
